        <mxCell id="ICEhqJMwdoexpDiNprW1-53" value="&lt;p style=&quot;margin:4px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Key Insight:&lt;/b&gt; Resources never import the adapters package.&lt;br&gt;They depend only on interfaces in &lt;code&gt;pkg/proxmox/&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;br&gt;The binding happens solely in &lt;code&gt;provider.go&lt;/code&gt; via constructor injection.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;VM is special:&lt;/b&gt; receives both &lt;code&gt;ProxmoxAdapter&lt;/code&gt; (as &lt;code&gt;Client&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;br&gt;and &lt;code&gt;VMAdapter&lt;/code&gt; (as &lt;code&gt;VMOperations&lt;/code&gt;) — two interface dependencies.&lt;/p&gt;" style="shape=note;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;size=14;verticalAlign=top;align=left;fillColor=#ffffcc;strokeColor=#999;fontSize=11;shadow=1;fontColor=#000000;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="1560" y="880" width="420" height="140" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="ICEhqJMwdoexpDiNprW1-54" value="&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-top:4px;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Legend&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-left:4px;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;- - -▷  «creates» / «uses» (factory)&lt;br&gt;───▶  «injected» (adapter → resource)&lt;br&gt;- - -▷  Dependency (resource → interface)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:#e1d5e7;padding:1px 4px;&quot;&gt;Purple&lt;/span&gt; Factory (provider.go)&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:#dae8fc;padding:1px 4px;&quot;&gt;Blue&lt;/span&gt; Central / VM classes&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:#d5e8d4;padding:1px 4px;&quot;&gt;Green&lt;/span&gt; CRUD adapters&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:#f5f5f5;padding:1px 4px;&quot;&gt;Grey&lt;/span&gt; Resource structs&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background:#fff2cc;padding:1px 4px;&quot;&gt;Yellow&lt;/span&gt; Config / Interfaces&lt;/p&gt;" style="verticalAlign=top;align=left;overflow=fill;fontSize=11;html=1;fillColor=#fff;strokeColor=#999;fontColor=#000000;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="230" y="950" width="340" height="180" as="geometry" />
